22 Wenyi Myit Rawng Ai Wa Byin Hkra Shakut U
Hpunau nauna ni hte kahkyin gumdin let arau jawm galaw ai kaw nna sharin la ai hku nna re.
Jaw ai, n jaw ai, hpaji rawng ai, n rawng ai hte seng nna shi gara hku mu mada ai lam hpe mung, anhte chye wa na re.
Persi hkawhkam gaw, dai bungli hpe tara shang pat shingdang tim, shanhte gaw nden marai hte nawku htingnu hpe bai gawgap ai.
Tsawra myit, kahkyin gumdin lam, makam masham hte Yehowa hpe shamyet shanat ai lam ni hpe mu lu wa ai majaw, uhpung uhpawng hku nna Yehowa galaw ya ai lam yawng hpe grau grau nna manu shadan mayu wa ai. "
Dai lam gaw anhte hpe "shi a hkang hta hkan nang" lu hkra karum ya nna "Hkristu zawn myit jasat" nga wa shangun ai. - 1 Petru 2: 21; 4: 1, NW.
Yoba ndai hku tsun ai: "Ngai hpe hpan da ai wa, shi hpe mung hpan da ai, n rai ni?"
Lit kaba lu ai hpunau nkau gaw, hpunau nauna ni ntsa sadi n dung mat sai ngu n jaw ai hku KGB ngu ai pyada ni shiga shapoi ai.
Myit Dum Poi garai n du shi ai aten hte, laksan hku nna dai shana hta anhte sumru ging ai.
Dai majaw, Yesu htet da ai lam yawng hpe galaw mayu ai Chyum ga sharin ni gaw, Yesu zawn tinang hkum tinang nyet kau ra ai.
Ma ni tinang myit hpe hkang lu ai atsam rawt jat na matu kanu kawa ni hpe gara lam ni gaw karum ya lu ai kun?
